<p><span class="location-text geolocation-title"><img src="/media/13073649/53252_85_years_web_banner_3.jpg" alt="Travel with confidence this summer" data-udi="umb://media/3721786b067d447b897e2f2aa1f5744a" /></span></p>
<p><span class="location-text geolocation-title">Celebrating 85 years’ experience with an additional £85 off per person*</span></p>
<p>To celebrate 85 years of inspiring holidays, we’re giving you, our valued guests, an additional £85 off per person when you book your summer 2019 break.</p>
<p>The offer can only be claimed at time of booking when you book by phone.</p>
<p><strong>So, to claim your additional £85 off per person, either:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Call us on 01483 938 355 to book your holiday and quote <strong>‘Inghams 85’</strong>: £85 per person will be removed from your total before payment</li>
<li>Book your holiday online without the discount, then email us at <a href="mailto:loyalty85@inghams.co.uk">loyalty85@inghams.co.uk</a> with your booking reference, and one of our team will be in touch to process a refund of £85 per person</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<div style="font-size: small;"><strong>*Terms and Conditions</strong><br /><span>Saving of £85 per person. Offer applicable to new bookings made from 22nd March 2019 only. Book by 30th April 2019.<br />Applicable to May to October 2019 departures for Inghams Lakes &amp; Mountains &amp; Inghams Italy.<br />Discount applies to adult prices only. Can be used in conjunction with existing offers.</span></div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
